/* # =================================================================
# Global selectors
# ================================================================= */

html {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  overflow-y: scroll; /* All browsers without overlaying scrollbars */
  -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; /* iOS 8+ */
}

*,
::before,
::after {
  background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Set `background-repeat: no-repeat` to all elements and pseudo elements */
  box-sizing: inherit;
}

::before,
::after {
  vertical-align: inherit;
  text-decoration: inherit; /* Inherit text-decoration and vertical align to ::before and ::after pseudo elements */
}

* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0; /* Reset `padding` and `margin` of all elements */
}

/* # =================================================================
# General elements
# ================================================================= */

/* Add the correct display in iOS 4-7.*/
audio:not([controls]) {
  display: none;
  height: 0;
}

hr {
  overflow: visible; /* Show the overflow in Edge and IE */
}

/*
* Correct `block` display not defined for any HTML5 element in IE 8/9
* Correct `block` display not defined for `details` or `summary` in IE 10/11
* and Firefox
* Correct `block` display not defined for `main` in IE 11
*/
article,
aside,
details,
figcaption,
figure,
footer,
header,
main,
menu,
nav,
section,
summary {
  display: block;
}

summary {
  display: list-item; /* Add the correct display in all browsers */
}

small {
  font-size: 80%; /* Set font-size to 80% in `small` elements */
}

[hidden],
template {
  display: none; /* Add the correct display in IE */
}

abbr[title] {
  border-bottom: 1px dotted; /* Add a bordered underline effect in all browsers */
  text-decoration: none; /* Remove text decoration in Firefox 40+ */
}

a {
  background-color: transparent; /* Remove the gray background on active links in IE 10 */
  -webkit-text-decoration-skip: objects; /* Remove gaps in links underline in iOS 8+ and Safari 8+ */
}

a:active,
a:hover {
  outline-width: 0; /* Remove the outline when hovering in all browsers */
}

code,
kbd,
pre,
samp {
  font-family: monospace, monospace; /* Specify the font family of code elements */
}

b,
strong {
  font-weight: bolder; /* Correct style set to `bold` in Edge 12+, Safari 6.2+, and Chrome 18+ */
}

dfn {
  font-style: italic; /* Address styling not present in Safari and Chrome */
}

/* Address styling not present in IE 8/9 */
mark {
  background-color: #ff0;
  color: #000;
}

/* https://gist.github.com/unruthless/413930 */
sub,
sup {
  position: relative;
  vertical-align: baseline;
  font-size: 75%;
  line-height: 0;
}

sub {
  bottom: -0.25em;
}

sup {
  top: -0.5em;
}

/* # =================================================================
# Forms
# ================================================================= */

input {
  border-radius: 0;
}

/* Apply cursor pointer to button elements */
button,
[type='button'],
[type='reset'],
[type='submit'],
[role='button'] {
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* Replace pointer cursor in disabled elements */
[disabled] {
  cursor: default;
}

[type='number'] {
  width: auto; /* Firefox 36+ */
}

[type='search'] {
  -webkit-appearance: textfield; /* Safari 8+ */
}

[type='search']::-webkit-search-cancel-button,
[type='search']::-webkit-search-decoration {
  -webkit-appearance: none; /* Safari 8 */
}

textarea {
  overflow: auto; /* Internet Explorer 11+ */
  resize: vertical; /* Specify textarea resizability */
}

button,
input,
optgroup,
select,
textarea {
  font: inherit; /* Specify font inheritance of form elements */
}

optgroup {
  font-weight: bold; /* Restore the font weight unset by the previous rule. */
}

button {
  overflow: visible; /* Address `overflow` set to `hidden` in IE 8/9/10/11 */
}

/* Remove inner padding and border in Firefox 4+ */
button::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='button']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='reset']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='submit']::-moz-focus-inner {
  padding: 0;
  border-style: 0;
}

/* Replace focus style removed in the border reset above */
button:-moz-focusring,
[type='button']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='reset']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='submit']::-moz-focus-inner {
  outline: 1px dotted ButtonText;
}

button,
html [type='button'],
[type='reset'],
[type='submit'] {
  -webkit-appearance: button; /* Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS */
}

button,
select {
  text-transform: none; /* Firefox 40+, Internet Explorer 11- */
}

/* Remove the default button styling in all browsers */
button,
input,
select,
textarea {
  background-color: transparent;
  border-style: none;
  color: inherit;
}

/* Style select like a standard input */
select {
  -moz-appearance: none; /* Firefox 36+ */
  -webkit-appearance: none; /* Chrome 41+ */
}

select::-ms-expand {
  display: none; /* Internet Explorer 11+ */
}

select::-ms-value {
  color: currentColor; /* Internet Explorer 11+ */
}

legend {
  display: table; /* Correct the text wrapping in Edge and IE */
  max-width: 100%; /* Correct the text wrapping in Edge and IE */
  border: 0; /* Correct `color` not being inherited in IE 8/9/10/11 */
  color: inherit; /* Correct the color inheritance from `fieldset` elements in IE */
  white-space: normal; /* Correct the text wrapping in Edge and IE */
}

::-webkit-file-upload-button {
  font: inherit; /* Change font properties to `inherit` in Chrome and Safari */
  -webkit-appearance: button; /* Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari */
}

[type='search'] {
  outline-offset: -2px; /* Correct the outline style in Safari */
  -webkit-appearance: textfield; /* Correct the odd appearance in Chrome and Safari */
}

/* # =================================================================
# Specify media element style
# ================================================================= */

img {
  display: inline-block;
  vertical-align: top;
  border-style: none; /* Remove border when inside `a` element in IE 8/9/10 */
}

/* Add the correct vertical alignment in Chrome, Firefox, and Opera */
progress {
  vertical-align: baseline;
}

svg:not(:root) {
  overflow: hidden; /* Internet Explorer 11- */
}

audio,
canvas,
progress,
video {
  display: inline-block; /* Internet Explorer 11+, Windows Phone 8.1+ */
}

/* Responsive media elements so that images and embeds scale with the browser width */
img,
embed,
object,
audio,
video {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

/* # =================================================================
# Accessibility
# ================================================================= */

/* Hide content from screens but not screenreaders */
@media screen {
  [hidden~='screen'] {
    display: inherit;
  }
  [hidden~='screen']:not(:active):not(:focus):not(:target) {
    position: absolute !important;
    clip: rect(0 0 0 0) !important;
  }
}

/* Specify the progress cursor of updating elements */
[aria-busy='true'] {
  cursor: progress;
}

/* Specify the pointer cursor of trigger elements */
[aria-controls] {
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* Specify the unstyled cursor of disabled, not-editable, or otherwise inoperable elements */
[aria-disabled] {
  cursor: default;
}

/* # =================================================================
# Selection
# ================================================================= */

/* Specify text selection background color and omit drop shadow */

::-moz-selection {
  background-color: #b3d4fc; /* Required when declaring ::selection */
  color: #000;
  text-shadow: none;
}

::selection {
  background-color: #b3d4fc; /* Required when declaring ::selection */
  color: #000;
  text-shadow: none;
}

/*!
 * Hamburgers
 * @description Tasty CSS-animated hamburgers
 * @author Jonathan Suh @jonsuh
 * @site https://jonsuh.com/hamburgers
 * @link https://github.com/jonsuh/hamburgers
 */

// Settings
// ==================================================
$hamburger-padding-x           : 12px !default;
$hamburger-padding-y           : 12px !default;
$hamburger-layer-width         : 28px !default;
$hamburger-layer-height        : 3px !default;
$hamburger-layer-spacing       : 6px !default;
$hamburger-layer-color         : #006472 !default;
$hamburger-layer-border-radius : 4px !default; 
$hamburger-hover-opacity       : 1 !default;
$hamburger-active-layer-color  : $hamburger-layer-color !default;
$hamburger-active-hover-opacity: $hamburger-hover-opacity !default;

// To use CSS filters as the hover effect instead of opacity,
// set $hamburger-hover-use-filter as true and
// change the value of $hamburger-hover-filter accordingly.
$hamburger-hover-use-filter   : false !default;
$hamburger-hover-filter       : opacity(50%) !default;
$hamburger-active-hover-filter: $hamburger-hover-filter !default;


// Hamburger
// ==================================================
.hamburger {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 0;
  padding: $hamburger-padding-y $hamburger-padding-x;
  overflow: visible;
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 0;
  color: inherit;

  // Normalize (<button>)
  font: inherit;
  text-transform: none;
  transition-duration: 0.15s;

  transition-property: opacity, filter;
  transition-timing-function: linear;
  cursor: pointer;

  &:hover {
    @if $hamburger-hover-use-filter == true {
      filter: $hamburger-hover-filter;
    }
    @else {
      opacity: $hamburger-hover-opacity;
    }
  }

  &.is-active {
    &:hover {
      @if $hamburger-hover-use-filter == true {
        filter: $hamburger-active-hover-filter;
      }
      @else {
        opacity: $hamburger-active-hover-opacity;
      }
    }

    .hamburger-inner,
    .hamburger-inner::before,
    .hamburger-inner::after {
      background-color: $hamburger-active-layer-color;
    }
  }
}

.hamburger-box {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  width: $hamburger-layer-width;
  height: $hamburger-layer-height * 3 + $hamburger-layer-spacing * 2;
}

.hamburger-inner {
  top: 50%;
  display: block;
  margin-top: $hamburger-layer-height / -2;

  &,
  &::before,
  &::after {
    position: absolute;
    width: $hamburger-layer-width;
    height: $hamburger-layer-height;
    background-color: $hamburger-layer-color;
    border-radius: $hamburger-layer-border-radius;
    transition-duration: 0.15s;
    transition-property: transform;
    transition-timing-function: ease;
  }

  &::before,
  &::after {
    display: block;
    content: '';
  }

  &::before {
    top: ($hamburger-layer-spacing + $hamburger-layer-height) * -1;
  }

  &::after {
    bottom: ($hamburger-layer-spacing + $hamburger-layer-height) * -1;
  }
}

// squeeze
/*
   * Squeeze
   */
.hamburger--squeeze {
  .hamburger-inner {
    transition-duration: 0.075s;
    transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.55, 0.055, 0.675, 0.19);

    &::before {
      transition: top 0.075s 0.12s ease,
        opacity 0.075s ease;
    }

    &::after {
      transition: bottom 0.075s 0.12s ease,
        transform 0.075s cubic-bezier(0.55, 0.055, 0.675, 0.19);
    }
  }

  &.is-active {
    .hamburger-inner {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
      transition-delay: 0.12s;
      transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1);

      &::before {
        top: 0;
        transition: top 0.075s ease,
          opacity 0.075s 0.12s ease;
        opacity: 0;
      }

      &::after {
        bottom: 0;
        transform: rotate(-90deg);
        transition: bottom 0.075s ease,
          transform 0.075s 0.12s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1);
      }
    }
  }
}","html {

","// standard clearfix
@mixin clearfix {
  &::before,
  &::after {
    content: ' ';
    display: table;
  }

  &::after {
    clear: both;
  }

  & {
    *zoom: 1;
  }
}

// aspect ratio mixin
@mixin aspect-ratio($arglist...) {
  $map: keywords($arglist);
  $height: map-get($map, height) or nth-or-null($arglist, 2);
  $width: map-get($map, width) or nth-or-null($arglist, 1);
  $ratio: map-get($map, ratio) or if($width and $height, $width/$height, nth-or-null($arglist, 1)) or 1;
  $padding: 1 / $ratio * 100%;

  &::before {
    content: '';
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    padding-bottom: $padding;
  }

  &::after {
    content: '';
    display: table;
  }
}

// Helper function
// Return null rather than throwing an error if index is outside list range.
@function nth-or-null($list, $index) {
  @return if(length($list) >= $index, nth($list, $index), null);
}

// remove default styles in iOS.
@mixin remove-webkit-defaults {
  border-radius: 0;
  appearance: none;
}

@function calculateRem($size) {
  $remSize: $size / 16;
  @return #{$remSize}rem;
}

// USAGE: @include font-size(font-size in px, line height in px); line-height optional
@mixin font-size($size, $line-height: false) {
  font-size: calculateRem($size);
  @if $line-height != false {
    line-height: ($line-height / $size);
  }
}

// USAGE: @include stagger-transition-delay(10, 0.5s, 0.1s);
@mixin stagger-transition-delay($i, $initial-delay, $stagger-delay) {
  @while $i > 0 {
    &:nth-child(#{$i}) {
      transition-delay: $initial-delay + $stagger-delay * $i;
    }

    $i: $i - 1;
  }
}

// USAGE: @include hocus {color: red;}
@mixin hocus {
  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    @content;
  }
}

// USAGE: @include wp-admin-offset(top, 0)

$wp-admin-bar-md: 32px;
$wp-admin-bar-sm: 48px;

$wp-breakpoint-md: 784px;
$wp-breakpoint-sm: 600px;

@mixin wp-admin-offset($prop: top, $offset: 0) {
  // No WP admin bar
  #{ $prop }: #{$offset};

  // WP admin bar is visible
  body.admin-bar & {
    // Medium-sized devices
    #{ $prop }: if($offset != 0, calc(#{$offset} + #{$wp-admin-bar-sm}), #{$wp-admin-bar-sm});

    // Larger devices
    @media (min-width: #{ $wp-breakpoint-md }) {
      #{ $prop }: if($offset != 0, calc(#{$offset} + #{$wp-admin-bar-md}), #{$wp-admin-bar-md});
    }

    // Mobile-ish sizes, the admin bar isn't sticky anymore
    @media (max-width: #{ $wp-breakpoint-sm }) {
      #{ $prop }: #{$offset};
    }
  }
}

@mixin image-with-focus {

  }
  &--left-top {

  }

  }

","//////////////////////////////
// Default Variables
//////////////////////////////
$Breakpoint-Settings: (
  'default media': all,
  'default feature': min-width,
  'default pair': width,

  'force all media type': false,
  'to ems': false,
  'transform resolutions': true,

  'no queries': false,
  'no query fallbacks': false,

  'base font size': 16px,

  'legacy syntax': false
);

$breakpoint: () !default;

//////////////////////////////
// Imports
//////////////////////////////
@import "breakpoint/settings";
@import 'breakpoint/context';
@import 'breakpoint/helpers';
@import 'breakpoint/parsers';
@import 'breakpoint/no-query';

@import 'breakpoint/respond-to';

@import "breakpoint/legacy-settings";

//////////////////////////////
// Breakpoint Mixin
//////////////////////////////

@mixin breakpoint($query, $no-query: false) {
  @include legacy-settings-warning;

  // Reset contexts
  @include private-breakpoint-reset-contexts();

  $breakpoint: breakpoint($query, false);

  $query-string: map-get($breakpoint, 'query');
  $query-fallback: map-get($breakpoint, 'fallback');

  $private-breakpoint-context-holder: map-get($breakpoint, 'context holder') !global;
  $private-breakpoint-query-count: map-get($breakpoint, 'query count') !global;

  // Allow for an as-needed override or usage of no query fallback.
  @if $no-query != false {
    $query-fallback: $no-query;
  }

  @if $query-fallback != false {
    $context-setter: private-breakpoint-set-context('no-query', $query-fallback);
  }

  // Print Out Query String
  @if not breakpoint-get('no queries') {
    @media #{$query-string} {
      @content;
    }
  }

  @if breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks') != false or breakpoint-get('no queries') == true {

    $type: type-of(breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks'));
    $print: false;

    @if ($type == 'bool') {
      $print: true;
    }
    @else if ($type == 'string') {
      @if $query-fallback == breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks') {
        $print: true;
      }
    }
    @else if ($type == 'list') {
      @each $wrapper in breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks') {
        @if $query-fallback == $wrapper {
          $print: true;
        }
      }
    }

    // Write Fallback
    @if ($query-fallback != false) and ($print == true) {
      $type-fallback: type-of($query-fallback);

      @if ($type-fallback != 'bool') {
        #{$query-fallback} & {
          @content;
        }
      }
      @else {
        @content;
      }
    }
  }

  @include private-breakpoint-reset-contexts();
}


@mixin mq($query, $no-query: false) {
  @include breakpoint($query, $no-query) {
    @content;
  }
}

","@mixin absolute-full {

  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
}

.c-hero-wrapper {

  }

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop-wider) {

  }

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop-xl) {

  }

.c-hero-wrapper__breadcrumb-height {

}

.c-hero {

    height: unset;

.hero-bottom-mobile-only {

// The background image options

.c-hero__background {

}

.c-hero__pattern-mobile {

  bottom: 0;
  z-index: 1;

  }
}

.c-hero__pattern-desktop {
  display: none;
  @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {

    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;

      z-index: -3;

      height: 100%;

  @media (min-width: $break-desktop-med) {

    }
  }
}

.c-hero__image {

  z-index: -1;

    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {

  }
}

.c-hero__image-filter {

.c-hero__doodle-wrapper {

.c-hero__doodle {

// The title text and form content

",".c-cta-button {

  margin-right: 15px;

  text-align: center;

  cursor: pointer;

  @include font-size(19);

  span {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;

    line-height: 1;
  }

    position: relative;

    font-style: normal;
  }
}

// plain buttons --- plain buttons --- plain buttons --- plain buttons ---
// button_type: "plain-on-teal"     or     button_type: "plain-on-white"     or     button_type: "plain-on-transparent     or     button_type: "plain-on-gold",
.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-white {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 2px solid $teal;
  color: $teal;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $teal;
    color: $white;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-white.active {
  background-color: $teal;
  color: $white;
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-teal {
  background-color: $teal;
  border: 2px solid $white;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    color: $teal;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-gold {
  background-color: $gold;
  border: 2px solid $gold;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    color: $white;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-transparent {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 2px solid $white;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $gold;
    border: 2px solid $gold;
    color: $teal;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--teal-on-transparent {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 2px solid $teal;
  color: $teal;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $teal;
    border: 2px solid $teal;
    color: $white;
  }
}

// arrow buttons --- arrow buttons --- arrow buttons --- arrow buttons ---
// button_type: "arrow-on-teal"   or       button_type: "arrow-on-white

.c-cta-button-type--arrow-on-white {
  position: relative;
  padding: 17px 54px 17px 24px;
  background-color: $white;
  border: 2px solid $teal;
  color: $teal;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $teal;
    color: $white;
  }
  span {
    z-index: 1;
    display: block;
  }

  &:after {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 24px;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--green.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }

  &:hover {
    &:after {
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--yellow.png');
    }
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--arrow-on-teal {
  position: relative;
  padding: 17px 54px 17px 24px;
  background-color: $teal;
  border: 2px solid $white;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    color: $teal;
  }

  span {
    z-index: 1;
  }

  &:after {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 24px;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--yellow.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }

  &:hover {
    border-color: $teal;

    &:after {
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--green.png');
    }
  }
}

// heart buttons --- heart buttons --- heart buttons --- heart buttons ---
//  button_type: "heart-on-gold"      0r           button_type: "heart-on-gold"

.c-cta-button-type--heart-on-gold {
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 0px;
  padding: 17px 44px 17px 14px;
  background-color: $gold;
  border: 2px solid $gold;
  color: $teal;

  @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
    padding: 17px 47px 17px 14px;
  }

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    border: 2px solid $white;
    color: $teal;
  }
  span {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: inline-block;
    &:after {
      position: absolute;
      top: -2px;
      right: -33px;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/heart--white.png');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center center;
      background-size: contain;
      content: '';
    }
  }

  &:hover {
    span {
      &:after {
        background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/heart--gold.png');
      }
    }
  }

  &.with-white-underline {
    span {
      &:after {
        top: 0px;
      }
    }
  }
}

// underlined buttons --- underlined buttons --- underlined buttons --- underlined buttons ---
//  button_type: "underline-on-teal"      0r           button_type: "underline-on-white"      0r           button_type: "underline-on-gold"

.c-cta-button-type--underline-on-gold {
  background-color: $gold;
  border: 2px solid $gold;
  color: $teal;
  span {
    position: relative;
    // display: inline-block;
    &:before {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -4px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3.2px;
      background-color: $white;
      border-radius: 3px;
      transform: rotate(-1deg);
      content: '';
    }
  }
  &:hover {
    background-color: $white;
    border: 2px solid $white;
    // span {
    //   &:before {
    //     background-color: $gold;
    //   }
    // }
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--underline-on-white {
  background-color: $teal;
  color: $white;

  span {
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid $gold;
  }
  &:hover {
    background-color: $dark-teal;
  }
}
.c-cta-button-type--underline-on-teal {
  background-color: $gold;
  color: $teal;

  span {
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid $white;
  }
  &:hover {
    background-color: $white;
    span {
      border-bottom: 3px solid $gold;
    }
  }
}

  }

    font-family: $font-headers;

    }
  }

    font-family: $font-headers;
    font-weight: 400;

      @include font-size(26, 32);
    }

      @include font-size(30, 35);
    }

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop-wide) {
      @include font-size(40, 48);
    }
  }

  .c-quote__copy {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  .c-quote__subtitle {
    @include font-size(19, 26);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-family: $font-text;

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
      @include font-size(19, 28);
    }
  }
}

.with-image {
  .c-quote__inner {
    padding: 40px 20px;

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
      padding: 130px 40px;
    }

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop-med) {
      padding: 130px 60px;
    }

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop-wide) {
      padding: 130px 100px;
    }

    &:after {
      display: none;
    }

  }

  .c-quote__content {
    width: 100%;
    margin-right: 0px;

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 59%;
      padding-top: 0px;
      padding-left: 0px;
    }
  }
}

.c-quote__image {
  position: relative;
  width: 65%;
  margin: 0px auto 30px auto;

  @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
    width: 41%;
    margin-bottom: 0px;
    padding-right: 65px;
  }

  img {
    border: 4px solid $white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transform: rotate(-3.16deg);

    @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
      border: 8px solid $white;
      border-radius: 16px;
    }
  }
}

.c-quote__button {
  .c-cta-button {
    margin-right: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
}
",".c-accordion__title {
  @include font-size(30, 33);
  max-width: 870px;
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-headers;
  text-align: left;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(40, 48);
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
}

.c-accordion__subtitle {
  @include font-size(19, 26);
  max-width: 870px;
  margin: 8px auto 24px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $lato;
  text-align: left;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(19, 28);
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }
}

.c-accordion {
  .o-container__text {
    margin: 0px auto;
  }

  .c-accordion__title-block {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
      padding-right: 150px;
      padding-left: 150px;
    }

    .c-accordion__title {
      position: relative;
    }

    .c-accordion__doodle-left {
      @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
        position: absolute;
        top: -25px;
        left: 0;
        width: 100px;
      }
    }

    .c-accordion__doodle-left img {
      @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }
    }

    .c-accordion__doodle-right {
      display: none;

      @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
        position: absolute;
        top: 40px;
        right: 0;
        display: block;
      }
    }
  }
}

.c-accordion__item {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  background-color: $lightest-teal;
  border-radius: 8px;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
}

.c-accordion__heading {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 16px 66px 16px 18px;
  font-family: $font-headers;
  text-align: left;
  transition: all 300ms;
  cursor: pointer;
  @include font-size(19, 23);

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding: 26px 66px 22px 24px;
    @include font-size(19, 24);
  }

  &:hover {
    .c-accordion__arrow {
      background-color: $gold;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/chevron-teal.png');
      border-color: $teal;
    }
  }

  &:active {
    .c-accordion__arrow {
      background-color: $gold;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/chevron-teal.png');
      border-color: $gold;
    }
  }

  &.show {
    .c-accordion__arrow {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
  }
}

.c-accordion__arrow {
  position: absolute;
  top: 13px;
  right: 16px;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/chevron-teal.png');
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
  background-size: 20px;
  transform: rotate(180deg);
  transition: color 300ms, background-color 300ms;
  pointer-events: none;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    top: 22px;
    right: 18px;
  }
}

.c-accordion__description {
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;

  transition: all 300ms;

  &-inner {
    padding: 10px 25px 18px 18px;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding: 10px 25px 25px 25px;
    }
  }

  p {
    @include font-size(19, 28);
    margin-top: 17px;
    margin-bottom: 0;

    &:first-of-type {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
  }

  ul,
  ol {
    @include font-size(16, 24);
    margin-top: 17px;
    margin-left: 17px;
  }

  a {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
}
",".c-donate__donation-type-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;

  a {
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
}

.c-donate__form {
  max-width: 425px;
  @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
    max-width: 425px;
  }
}

.c-donate__donation-type {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  height: 60px;
  padding: 1rem;
  background-color: $white;
  color: $blue;
  text-align: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  @include font-size(19, 20);

  &--active {
    background-color: #bfe8f0;
    color: $teal;
  }

  &:hover {
    background-color: $white;
    color: $teal;
  }
}

.c-donate__donation-type--regular {
  flex-basis: calc(50% - 8px);

  &.only {
    flex-basis: 100%;
  }
}

.c-donate__donation-type--one-off {
  flex-basis: 50%;
  &.only {
    flex-basis: 100%;
  }
}

.c-donate__option-wrapper {
  display: none;

  &--active {
    display: block;
  }
}

.c-donate__amount-options-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

.c-donate__one-off-item,
.c-donate__regular-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-basis: calc(25% - 6px);
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 100%;
  height: 60px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  padding: 1rem 0;
  background-color: $white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $blue;
  text-align: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  @include font-size(19, 20);

  &:hover {
    background-color: #bfe8f0;
    color: $teal;
  }
}

.c-donate__one-off-item--active,
.c-donate__regular-item--active {
  background-color: #bfe8f0;
  color: $teal;
}

.c-donate__validate-message {
  margin-top: 5px;
  @include font-size(14);
}

.c-donate__any-regular-amount-input-wrapper,
.c-donate__any-one-off-amount-input-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  display: none;
  width: 100%;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  text-align: left;

  &.is-active {
    display: block;
  }

  i {
    position: absolute;
    top: 48px;
    display: block;
    width: 25px;
    color: $blue;
    font-family: $font-headers;
    text-align: center;
    transform: translate(0, -50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
}

.c-donate__any-regular-amount-input,
.c-donate__any-one-off-amount-input {
  width: 100%;
  height: 45px;
  padding-left: 2rem;
  background-color: $white;
  border: 1px solid $white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $base-black;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(16);
  @include breakpoint($break-tablet) {
    @include font-size(20);
  }

  &::placeholder {
    color: $white;
    font-family: $font-text;
    font-weight: normal;
  }

  &.invalid-missing-amount {
    border: 2px solid $teal;
    &::placeholder {
      color: $teal;
    }
  }
}

.c-donate__display-inner {
  display: none;

  &.is-active {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 48px;
    margin-top: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding: 8px;
    background-color: $light-gold;
    border-radius: 100px;

    &:before {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: calc(12.5% - 23.5px);
      width: 47px;
      height: 16px;
      margin-top: -15px;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/chestnut-tree-house/assets/src/images/donate-text-bubble.svg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: bottom center;
      background-size: contain;
      content: '';
    }

    &[data-donation-option='2'] {
      &:before {
        left: calc(37.5% - 23.5px);
      }
    }

    &[data-donation-option='3'] {
      &:before {
        left: calc(62.5% - 23.5px);
      }
    }
  }
}

.c-donate__display-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
}

.c-donate__display-text {
  padding: 0 10px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  line-height: 1.3;
  @include font-size(19, 28);
}

.c-donate__submit-button {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 100%;
  height: 60px;
  background-color: $blue;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $white;
  @include font-size(19, 20);

  span {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;

    i {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      font-style: normal;
    }

    &:before {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -6px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3.2px;
      background-color: $white;
      border-radius: 3px;
      transform: rotate(-1deg);
      content: '';
    }

    &:after {
      position: absolute;
      top: -2px;
      right: -30px;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/heart--white.png');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center center;
      background-size: contain;
      content: '';
    }
  }
}
",".c-donate {
  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
  }
}

.c-donate__content-wrapper {
  @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    width: 50%;
  }
}

.c-donate__content {
  width: calc(100% - 32px);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 30px 0;
  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    width: calc(100% - 16px);
    max-width: 425px;
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 80px 10px;
    padding-right: 16px;
  }
}

.c-donate__image {
  display: none;
  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex: 1;
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  img {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
}

.c-donate__tag {
  @include font-size(19, 22);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  font-weight: normal;
}

.c-donate__title {
  margin-bottom: 11px;

  font-weight: normal;

  @include font-size(30, 33);

  @media (min-width: $break-desktop-med) {
    @include font-size(40, 48);
  }
}

.c-donate__description {
  margin-bottom: 23px;
  font-family: $font-text;

  p {
    @include font-size(19, 28);
    font-weight: normal;
  }
}
",".c-listing__results {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: $blue;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(19);

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }
}

.c-listings__cards {
  margin: 0 16px;
  scroll-margin-top: 215px;

  @media (min-width: 400px) {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin: 0 -8px;
  }

  @media (min-width: $break-mobile-nav) {
    scroll-margin-top: 265px;
  }

}

// lisintg page with a map

.c-listing-map-top-bar {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  scroll-margin-top: 110px;

  @media (min-width: $break-tablet) {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  @media (min-width: $break-mobile-nav) {
    scroll-margin-top: 180px;
  }

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-top: 0px;
  }

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop-wider) {
    margin-top: -40px;
  }

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop-xl) {
    margin-top: -60px;
  }
}

.c-listing-map-top-bar__results {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: $blue;
  font-family: $font-text;
  font-size: 19px;
  visibility: visible;
  filter: brightness(0.8);
  @media (min-width: $break-tablet) {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  &--hidden {
    visibility: hidden;
  }
}

.c-listing-map-top-bar__buttons {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  @media (min-width: $break-tablet) {
  }
}

.c-listing-map-top-bar__button-list,
.c-listing-map-top-bar__button-map {
  margin-bottom: 0;
  a {
    margin: 0 10px 0 0;
    padding: 17px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  @media (min-width: $break-tablet) {
    a {
      padding: 20px 24px;
    }
  }
}

// can't use display: none here to hide map, as it will not load correctly, using max-height instead
.c-listing-map__listings,
.c-listing-map__map {
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  &--active {
    max-height: 100%;
  }
}
",".c-card {
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  padding: 0 8px;
  text-decoration: none;

  @media (min-width: 400px) {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
    max-width: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: $break-tablet) {
    flex: 1 1 33%;
    max-width: 33%;
  }

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    flex: 1 1 25%;
    max-width: 25%;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
}

.c-card:last-child {
  margin-right: auto;
}

.c-card__inner {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 2px solid $light-grey;
  border-radius: 16px;
  transition: all 200ms;
}

.c-card__image {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 0;
  padding-bottom: 50%;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding-bottom: 60%;
  }

  &:after {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba($light-gold, 0.4);
    transition: all 200ms;
    opacity: 0;
    content: '';
  }
}

.c-card__actual-image {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.c-card__start-date {
  padding: 16px 80% 16px 16px;
  background-color: #bfe8f0;
  background-size: cover;
  color: $blue;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: all 200ms;
  @include font-size(56, 54);

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(72, 80);
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  &--image {
    background-color: unset;
    color: $white;
  }
}

.c-card__meta {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.c-card__terms {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
}

.c-card__term {
  margin-right: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  background-color: $light-gold;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(16, 20);
}

.c-card__charity {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 4px;
  margin-right: 8px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  background-color: $gold;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(16, 20);

    background-color: $teal;
    color: $white;
  }

.c-card__location {
  @include font-size(16, 20);
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding: 8px 8px 0 24px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding-top: 12px;
  }

  &--onsite,
  &--virtual {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: contain;
  }

  &--onsite {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/address.svg');
  }

  &--virtual {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/virtual.svg');
  }

.c-card__content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  flex-grow: 1;
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 16px;
  padding-top: 32px;
  transition: all 200ms;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding-right: 24px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }
}

.c-card__header {
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  color: $blue;
  @include font-size(19, 22);

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(24, 28);
  }
}

.c-card__excerpt {
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(19, 26);

  p {
    @include font-size(19, 26);
  }
}

.c-card__address,
.c-card__opening-times {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding-left: 28px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(16, 20);

  &:before {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-right: 10px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }
}

.c-card__address {
  margin-top:12px;
  &:before {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/address.svg');
  }
}

.c-card__opening-times {
  &:before {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/times.svg');
  }
}

.c-card__date {
  color: $teal;
  @include font-size(14, 18);
  font-family: $font-text;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(16, 20);
  }
}

.c-card__cta {
  display: flex;
  flex-basis:100%;
  align-items: flex-end;
  color: $blue;
  font-family: $font-text;
  font-weight: bold;
  @include font-size(19, 28);

  &:after {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-left: 10px;
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/cta-arrow.svg');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }
}

.c-card:hover {
  .c-card__inner {
    border-color: $blue;
  }

  .c-card__image {
    &:after {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .c-card__start-date {
    background-color: #bfe8f0;
  }

  .c-card__content {
    background-color: rgba($gold, 0.1);
  }
}

.c-card--2 {
  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
    max-width: 50%;
  }

  .c-card__image {
    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding-bottom: 190px;
    }
  }
}

.c-card--3 {
  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    flex: 1 1 33.33%;
    max-width: 33.33%;
  }

  .c-card__image {
    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding-bottom: 190px;
    }
  }
}

.c-card--long {
  display: block;
  flex: none;
  max-width: none;
  margin-bottom: 55px;

  .c-card__inner {
    flex-direction: row;
    height: auto;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .c-card__start-date,
  .c-card__image {
    display: none;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 244px;
      min-width: 244px;
      height: 182px;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
  }

  .c-card__content {
    padding: 0 8px;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding: 0 40px;
      border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    }
  }

  .c-card__header {
    @include font-size(24, 32);

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      @include font-size(32, 40);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
  }

  .c-card__excerpt {
    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
  }

  .c-card__type {
    display: inline-block;
    float: left;
    padding: 2px 8px 3px;
    background-color: $light-blue;
    border-radius: 5px;
    color: $teal;
    font-family: $font-text;
    @include font-size(16, 24);
  }

  .c-card__date {
    @include font-size(16, 28);
    float: left;
    margin-left: 24px;
  }
}

.c-card-event {
  position: relative;
}

.c-card-event__image-filter {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  z-index: -1;
  background-color: rgba($black, 0.2);
}

.c-card-event__image {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  z-index: -2;

    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

",".c-pagination {
  max-width: 1320px;
  margin: 20px auto 30px;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-top: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
}

.c-pagination__list {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 12px;
  list-style: none;
}

.c-pagination__button {
  margin: 0 4px;

  a, span, button {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 60px;
    padding: 0 25px;
    background-color: $light-gold;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: $teal;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 200ms;
  }

  &:not(.disabled) {
    a, span, button {
      &:hover, &.current {
        background-color: $gold;
      }
    }
  }

  &.disabled {
    a, span, button {
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
  }

  i {
    display: none;
    font-style: normal;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      display: inline;
    }
  }
}

.c-pagination__number {
  display: none;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    display: flex;
  }
}

.c-pagination__prev, .c-pagination__next {
  width: 50%;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    width: auto;
  }

  a, button {
    width: 100%;

    &:before, &:after {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/chestnut-tree-house/assets/src/images/btn_arrow.svg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center;
      background-size: contain;
      content: '';
    }
  }
}

.c-pagination__prev {
  a, button {
    &:before {
      margin-right: 14px;
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    &:after {
      display: none;
    }
  }
}

.c-pagination__next {
  a, button {
    &:before {
      display: none;
    }

    &:after {
      margin-left: 14px;
    }
  }
}

.c-sticky-donate__inner {

    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/icon-sticky-down.svg');

    align-items: center;

    width: 360px;
    height: 80px;
    margin-left: -180px;

    border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0;

    &:after {

      margin-left: 50px;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/icon-sticky-down.svg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: contain;

/* # =================================================================
# Global selectors
# ================================================================= */

html {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  overflow-y: scroll; /* All browsers without overlaying scrollbars */
  -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; /* iOS 8+ */
}

*,
::before,
::after {
  background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Set `background-repeat: no-repeat` to all elements and pseudo elements */
  box-sizing: inherit;
}

::before,
::after {
  vertical-align: inherit;
  text-decoration: inherit; /* Inherit text-decoration and vertical align to ::before and ::after pseudo elements */
}

* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0; /* Reset `padding` and `margin` of all elements */
}

/* # =================================================================
# General elements
# ================================================================= */

/* Add the correct display in iOS 4-7.*/
audio:not([controls]) {
  display: none;
  height: 0;
}

hr {
  overflow: visible; /* Show the overflow in Edge and IE */
}

/*
* Correct `block` display not defined for any HTML5 element in IE 8/9
* Correct `block` display not defined for `details` or `summary` in IE 10/11
* and Firefox
* Correct `block` display not defined for `main` in IE 11
*/
article,
aside,
details,
figcaption,
figure,
footer,
header,
main,
menu,
nav,
section,
summary {
  display: block;
}

summary {
  display: list-item; /* Add the correct display in all browsers */
}

small {
  font-size: 80%; /* Set font-size to 80% in `small` elements */
}

[hidden],
template {
  display: none; /* Add the correct display in IE */
}

abbr[title] {
  border-bottom: 1px dotted; /* Add a bordered underline effect in all browsers */
  text-decoration: none; /* Remove text decoration in Firefox 40+ */
}

a {
  background-color: transparent; /* Remove the gray background on active links in IE 10 */
  -webkit-text-decoration-skip: objects; /* Remove gaps in links underline in iOS 8+ and Safari 8+ */
}

a:active,
a:hover {
  outline-width: 0; /* Remove the outline when hovering in all browsers */
}

code,
kbd,
pre,
samp {
  font-family: monospace, monospace; /* Specify the font family of code elements */
}

b,
strong {
  font-weight: bolder; /* Correct style set to `bold` in Edge 12+, Safari 6.2+, and Chrome 18+ */
}

dfn {
  font-style: italic; /* Address styling not present in Safari and Chrome */
}

/* Address styling not present in IE 8/9 */
mark {
  background-color: #ff0;
  color: #000;
}

/* https://gist.github.com/unruthless/413930 */
sub,
sup {
  position: relative;
  vertical-align: baseline;
  font-size: 75%;
  line-height: 0;
}

sub {
  bottom: -0.25em;
}

sup {
  top: -0.5em;
}

/* # =================================================================
# Forms
# ================================================================= */

input {
  border-radius: 0;
}

/* Apply cursor pointer to button elements */
button,
[type='button'],
[type='reset'],
[type='submit'],
[role='button'] {
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* Replace pointer cursor in disabled elements */
[disabled] {
  cursor: default;
}

[type='number'] {
  width: auto; /* Firefox 36+ */
}

[type='search'] {
  -webkit-appearance: textfield; /* Safari 8+ */
}

[type='search']::-webkit-search-cancel-button,
[type='search']::-webkit-search-decoration {
  -webkit-appearance: none; /* Safari 8 */
}

textarea {
  overflow: auto; /* Internet Explorer 11+ */
  resize: vertical; /* Specify textarea resizability */
}

button,
input,
optgroup,
select,
textarea {
  font: inherit; /* Specify font inheritance of form elements */
}

optgroup {
  font-weight: bold; /* Restore the font weight unset by the previous rule. */
}

button {
  overflow: visible; /* Address `overflow` set to `hidden` in IE 8/9/10/11 */
}

/* Remove inner padding and border in Firefox 4+ */
button::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='button']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='reset']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='submit']::-moz-focus-inner {
  padding: 0;
  border-style: 0;
}

/* Replace focus style removed in the border reset above */
button:-moz-focusring,
[type='button']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='reset']::-moz-focus-inner,
[type='submit']::-moz-focus-inner {
  outline: 1px dotted ButtonText;
}

button,
html [type='button'],
[type='reset'],
[type='submit'] {
  -webkit-appearance: button; /* Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS */
}

button,
select {
  text-transform: none; /* Firefox 40+, Internet Explorer 11- */
}

/* Remove the default button styling in all browsers */
button,
input,
select,
textarea {
  background-color: transparent;
  border-style: none;
  color: inherit;
}

/* Style select like a standard input */
select {
  -moz-appearance: none; /* Firefox 36+ */
  -webkit-appearance: none; /* Chrome 41+ */
}

select::-ms-expand {
  display: none; /* Internet Explorer 11+ */
}

select::-ms-value {
  color: currentColor; /* Internet Explorer 11+ */
}

legend {
  display: table; /* Correct the text wrapping in Edge and IE */
  max-width: 100%; /* Correct the text wrapping in Edge and IE */
  border: 0; /* Correct `color` not being inherited in IE 8/9/10/11 */
  color: inherit; /* Correct the color inheritance from `fieldset` elements in IE */
  white-space: normal; /* Correct the text wrapping in Edge and IE */
}

::-webkit-file-upload-button {
  font: inherit; /* Change font properties to `inherit` in Chrome and Safari */
  -webkit-appearance: button; /* Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari */
}

[type='search'] {
  outline-offset: -2px; /* Correct the outline style in Safari */
  -webkit-appearance: textfield; /* Correct the odd appearance in Chrome and Safari */
}

/* # =================================================================
# Specify media element style
# ================================================================= */

img {
  display: inline-block;
  vertical-align: top;
  border-style: none; /* Remove border when inside `a` element in IE 8/9/10 */
}

/* Add the correct vertical alignment in Chrome, Firefox, and Opera */
progress {
  vertical-align: baseline;
}

svg:not(:root) {
  overflow: hidden; /* Internet Explorer 11- */
}

audio,
canvas,
progress,
video {
  display: inline-block; /* Internet Explorer 11+, Windows Phone 8.1+ */
}

/* Responsive media elements so that images and embeds scale with the browser width */
img,
embed,
object,
audio,
video {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

/* # =================================================================
# Accessibility
# ================================================================= */

/* Hide content from screens but not screenreaders */
@media screen {
  [hidden~='screen'] {
    display: inherit;
  }
  [hidden~='screen']:not(:active):not(:focus):not(:target) {
    position: absolute !important;
    clip: rect(0 0 0 0) !important;
  }
}

/* Specify the progress cursor of updating elements */
[aria-busy='true'] {
  cursor: progress;
}

/* Specify the pointer cursor of trigger elements */
[aria-controls] {
  cursor: pointer;
}

/*!
 * Hamburgers
 * @description Tasty CSS-animated hamburgers
 * @author Jonathan Suh @jonsuh
 * @site https://jonsuh.com/hamburgers
 * @link https://github.com/jonsuh/hamburgers
 */

// Settings
// ==================================================
$hamburger-padding-x           : 12px !default;
$hamburger-padding-y           : 12px !default;
$hamburger-layer-width         : 28px !default;
$hamburger-layer-height        : 3px !default;
$hamburger-layer-spacing       : 6px !default;
$hamburger-layer-color         : #006472 !default;
$hamburger-layer-border-radius : 4px !default; 
$hamburger-hover-opacity       : 1 !default;
$hamburger-active-layer-color  : $hamburger-layer-color !default;
$hamburger-active-hover-opacity: $hamburger-hover-opacity !default;

// To use CSS filters as the hover effect instead of opacity,
// set $hamburger-hover-use-filter as true and
// change the value of $hamburger-hover-filter accordingly.
$hamburger-hover-use-filter   : false !default;
$hamburger-hover-filter       : opacity(50%) !default;
$hamburger-active-hover-filter: $hamburger-hover-filter !default;


// Hamburger
// ==================================================
.hamburger {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 0;
  padding: $hamburger-padding-y $hamburger-padding-x;
  overflow: visible;
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 0;
  color: inherit;

  // Normalize (<button>)
  font: inherit;
  text-transform: none;
  transition-duration: 0.15s;

  transition-property: opacity, filter;
  transition-timing-function: linear;
  cursor: pointer;

  &:hover {
    @if $hamburger-hover-use-filter == true {
      filter: $hamburger-hover-filter;
    }
    @else {
      opacity: $hamburger-hover-opacity;
    }
  }

  &.is-active {
    &:hover {
      @if $hamburger-hover-use-filter == true {
        filter: $hamburger-active-hover-filter;
      }
      @else {
        opacity: $hamburger-active-hover-opacity;
      }
    }

    .hamburger-inner,
    .hamburger-inner::before,
    .hamburger-inner::after {
      background-color: $hamburger-active-layer-color;
    }
  }
}

.hamburger-box {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  width: $hamburger-layer-width;
  height: $hamburger-layer-height * 3 + $hamburger-layer-spacing * 2;
}

.hamburger-inner {
  top: 50%;
  display: block;
  margin-top: $hamburger-layer-height / -2;

  &,
  &::before,
  &::after {
    position: absolute;
    width: $hamburger-layer-width;
    height: $hamburger-layer-height;
    background-color: $hamburger-layer-color;
    border-radius: $hamburger-layer-border-radius;
    transition-duration: 0.15s;
    transition-property: transform;
    transition-timing-function: ease;
  }

  &::before,
  &::after {
    display: block;
    content: '';
  }

  &::before {
    top: ($hamburger-layer-spacing + $hamburger-layer-height) * -1;
  }

  &::after {
    bottom: ($hamburger-layer-spacing + $hamburger-layer-height) * -1;
  }
}

// squeeze
/*
   * Squeeze
   */
.hamburger--squeeze {
  .hamburger-inner {
    transition-duration: 0.075s;
    transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.55, 0.055, 0.675, 0.19);

    &::before {
      transition: top 0.075s 0.12s ease,
        opacity 0.075s ease;
    }

    &::after {
      transition: bottom 0.075s 0.12s ease,
        transform 0.075s cubic-bezier(0.55, 0.055, 0.675, 0.19);
    }
  }

  &.is-active {
    .hamburger-inner {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
      transition-delay: 0.12s;
      transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1);

      &::before {
        top: 0;
        transition: top 0.075s ease,
          opacity 0.075s 0.12s ease;
        opacity: 0;
      }

      &::after {
        bottom: 0;
        transform: rotate(-90deg);
        transition: bottom 0.075s ease,
          transform 0.075s 0.12s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1);
      }
    }
  }
}","html {

@mixin clearfix {
  &::before,
  &::after {
    content: ' ';

  }

    clear: both;

  & {
    *zoom: 1;
  }
}

// aspect ratio mixin
@mixin aspect-ratio($arglist...) {
  $map: keywords($arglist);
  $height: map-get($map, height) or nth-or-null($arglist, 2);
  $width: map-get($map, width) or nth-or-null($arglist, 1);
  $ratio: map-get($map, ratio) or if($width and $height, $width/$height, nth-or-null($arglist, 1)) or 1;
  $padding: 1 / $ratio * 100%;

  &::before {
    content: '';
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    padding-bottom: $padding;
  }

  &::after {
    content: '';
    display: table;
  }
}

// Helper function
// Return null rather than throwing an error if index is outside list range.
@function nth-or-null($list, $index) {
  @return if(length($list) >= $index, nth($list, $index), null);
}

// remove default styles in iOS.
@mixin remove-webkit-defaults {
  border-radius: 0;
  appearance: none;
}

@function calculateRem($size) {
  $remSize: $size / 16;
  @return #{$remSize}rem;
}

// USAGE: @include font-size(font-size in px, line height in px); line-height optional
@mixin font-size($size, $line-height: false) {
  font-size: calculateRem($size);
  @if $line-height != false {
    line-height: ($line-height / $size);
  }
}

// USAGE: @include stagger-transition-delay(10, 0.5s, 0.1s);
@mixin stagger-transition-delay($i, $initial-delay, $stagger-delay) {
  @while $i > 0 {
    &:nth-child(#{$i}) {
      transition-delay: $initial-delay + $stagger-delay * $i;
    }

    $i: $i - 1;
  }
}

// USAGE: @include hocus {color: red;}
@mixin hocus {
  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    @content;
  }
}

// USAGE: @include wp-admin-offset(top, 0)

$wp-admin-bar-md: 32px;
$wp-admin-bar-sm: 48px;

$wp-breakpoint-md: 784px;
$wp-breakpoint-sm: 600px;

@mixin wp-admin-offset($prop: top, $offset: 0) {
  // No WP admin bar
  #{ $prop }: #{$offset};

  // WP admin bar is visible
  body.admin-bar & {
    // Medium-sized devices
    #{ $prop }: if($offset != 0, calc(#{$offset} + #{$wp-admin-bar-sm}), #{$wp-admin-bar-sm});

    // Larger devices
    @media (min-width: #{ $wp-breakpoint-md }) {
      #{ $prop }: if($offset != 0, calc(#{$offset} + #{$wp-admin-bar-md}), #{$wp-admin-bar-md});
    }

    // Mobile-ish sizes, the admin bar isn't sticky anymore
    @media (max-width: #{ $wp-breakpoint-sm }) {
      #{ $prop }: #{$offset};
    }
  }
}

@mixin image-with-focus {
  img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  &--left-top {
    img {
      object-position: left top;
    }
  }

  &--center-top {
    img {
      object-position: center top;
    }
  }

  &--right-top {
    img {
      object-position: right top;
    }
  }

  &--left-center {
    img {
      object-position: left center;
    }
  }

  &--center-center {
    img {
      object-position: center center;
    }
  }

  &--right-center {
    img {
      object-position: right center;
    }
  }

  &--left-bottom {
    img {
      object-position: left bottom;
    }
  }

  &--center-bottom {
    img {
      object-position: center bottom;
    }
  }

  &--right-bottom {
    img {
      object-position: right bottom;
    }
  }
}

","//////////////////////////////
// Default Variables
//////////////////////////////
$Breakpoint-Settings: (
  'default media': all,
  'default feature': min-width,
  'default pair': width,

  'force all media type': false,
  'to ems': false,
  'transform resolutions': true,

  'no queries': false,
  'no query fallbacks': false,

  'base font size': 16px,

  'legacy syntax': false
);

$breakpoint: () !default;

//////////////////////////////
// Imports
//////////////////////////////
@import "breakpoint/settings";
@import 'breakpoint/context';
@import 'breakpoint/helpers';
@import 'breakpoint/parsers';
@import 'breakpoint/no-query';

@import 'breakpoint/respond-to';

@import "breakpoint/legacy-settings";

//////////////////////////////
// Breakpoint Mixin
//////////////////////////////

@mixin breakpoint($query, $no-query: false) {
  @include legacy-settings-warning;

  // Reset contexts
  @include private-breakpoint-reset-contexts();

  $breakpoint: breakpoint($query, false);

  $query-string: map-get($breakpoint, 'query');
  $query-fallback: map-get($breakpoint, 'fallback');

  $private-breakpoint-context-holder: map-get($breakpoint, 'context holder') !global;
  $private-breakpoint-query-count: map-get($breakpoint, 'query count') !global;

  // Allow for an as-needed override or usage of no query fallback.
  @if $no-query != false {
    $query-fallback: $no-query;
  }

  @if $query-fallback != false {
    $context-setter: private-breakpoint-set-context('no-query', $query-fallback);
  }

  // Print Out Query String
  @if not breakpoint-get('no queries') {
    @media #{$query-string} {
      @content;
    }
  }

  @if breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks') != false or breakpoint-get('no queries') == true {

    $type: type-of(breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks'));
    $print: false;

    @if ($type == 'bool') {
      $print: true;
    }
    @else if ($type == 'string') {
      @if $query-fallback == breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks') {
        $print: true;
      }
    }
    @else if ($type == 'list') {
      @each $wrapper in breakpoint-get('no query fallbacks') {
        @if $query-fallback == $wrapper {
          $print: true;
        }
      }
    }

    // Write Fallback
    @if ($query-fallback != false) and ($print == true) {
      $type-fallback: type-of($query-fallback);

      @if ($type-fallback != 'bool') {
        #{$query-fallback} & {
          @content;
        }
      }
      @else {
        @content;
      }
    }
  }

  @include private-breakpoint-reset-contexts();
}


@mixin mq($query, $no-query: false) {
  @include breakpoint($query, $no-query) {
    @content;
  }
}

// plain buttons --- plain buttons --- plain buttons --- plain buttons ---
// button_type: "plain-on-teal"     or     button_type: "plain-on-white"     or     button_type: "plain-on-transparent     or     button_type: "plain-on-gold",
.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-white {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 2px solid $teal;
  color: $teal;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $teal;
    color: $white;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-white.active {
  background-color: $teal;
  color: $white;
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-teal {
  background-color: $teal;
  border: 2px solid $white;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    color: $teal;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-gold {
  background-color: $gold;
  border: 2px solid $gold;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    color: $white;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--plain-on-transparent {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 2px solid $white;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $gold;
    border: 2px solid $gold;
    color: $teal;
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--teal-on-transparent {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 2px solid $teal;
  color: $teal;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $teal;
    border: 2px solid $teal;
    color: $white;
  }
}

// arrow buttons --- arrow buttons --- arrow buttons --- arrow buttons ---
// button_type: "arrow-on-teal"   or       button_type: "arrow-on-white

.c-cta-button-type--arrow-on-white {
  position: relative;
  padding: 17px 54px 17px 24px;
  background-color: $white;
  border: 2px solid $teal;
  color: $teal;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $teal;
    color: $white;
  }
  span {
    z-index: 1;
    display: block;
  }

  &:after {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 24px;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--green.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }

  &:hover {
    &:after {
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--yellow.png');
    }
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--arrow-on-teal {
  position: relative;
  padding: 17px 54px 17px 24px;
  background-color: $teal;
  border: 2px solid $white;
  color: $white;

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    color: $teal;
  }

  span {
    z-index: 1;
  }

  &:after {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 24px;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--yellow.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }

  &:hover {
    border-color: $teal;

    &:after {
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/arrow--green.png');
    }
  }
}

// heart buttons --- heart buttons --- heart buttons --- heart buttons ---
//  button_type: "heart-on-gold"      0r           button_type: "heart-on-gold"

.c-cta-button-type--heart-on-gold {
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 0px;
  padding: 17px 44px 17px 14px;
  background-color: $gold;
  border: 2px solid $gold;
  color: $teal;

  @media (min-width: $break-desktop) {
    padding: 17px 47px 17px 14px;
  }

  &:hover,
  &:focus {
    background-color: $white;
    border: 2px solid $white;
    color: $teal;
  }
  span {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: inline-block;
    &:after {
      position: absolute;
      top: -2px;
      right: -33px;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/heart--white.png');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center center;
      background-size: contain;
      content: '';
    }
  }

  &:hover {
    span {
      &:after {
        background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/icons/heart--gold.png');
      }
    }
  }

  &.with-white-underline {
    span {
      &:after {
        top: 0px;
      }
    }
  }
}

// underlined buttons --- underlined buttons --- underlined buttons --- underlined buttons ---
//  button_type: "underline-on-teal"      0r           button_type: "underline-on-white"      0r           button_type: "underline-on-gold"

.c-cta-button-type--underline-on-gold {
  background-color: $gold;
  border: 2px solid $gold;
  color: $teal;
  span {
    position: relative;
    // display: inline-block;
    &:before {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -4px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3.2px;
      background-color: $white;
      border-radius: 3px;
      transform: rotate(-1deg);
      content: '';
    }
  }
  &:hover {
    background-color: $white;
    border: 2px solid $white;
    // span {
    //   &:before {
    //     background-color: $gold;
    //   }
    // }
  }
}

.c-cta-button-type--underline-on-white {
  background-color: $teal;
  color: $white;

  span {
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid $gold;
  }
  &:hover {
    background-color: $dark-teal;
  }
}
.c-cta-button-type--underline-on-teal {
  background-color: $gold;
  color: $teal;

  span {
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid $white;
  }
  &:hover {
    background-color: $white;
    span {
      border-bottom: 3px solid $gold;
    }
  }
}

",".c-accordion__title {
  @include font-size(30, 33);

  margin: 0 0 8px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-headers;
  text-align: left;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(40, 48);
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
}

.c-accordion__subtitle {
  @include font-size(19, 26);
  max-width: 870px;
  margin: 8px auto 24px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $lato;
  text-align: left;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(19, 28);
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }
}

.c-accordion {
  .o-container__text {
    margin: 0px auto;
  }

  .c-accordion__title-block {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
      padding-right: 150px;
      padding-left: 150px;
    }

    .c-accordion__title {
      position: relative;
    }

    .c-accordion__doodle-left {
      @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
        position: absolute;
        top: -25px;
        left: 0;
        width: 100px;
      }
    }

    .c-accordion__doodle-left img {
      @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }
    }

    .c-accordion__doodle-right {
      display: none;

      @include breakpoint($break-desktop-med) {
        position: absolute;
        top: 40px;
        right: 0;
        display: block;
      }
    }
  }
}

.c-accordion__item {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  background-color: $lightest-teal;
  border-radius: 8px;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
}

.c-accordion__heading {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 16px 66px 16px 18px;
  font-family: $font-headers;
  text-align: left;
  transition: all 300ms;
  cursor: pointer;
  @include font-size(19, 23);

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding: 26px 66px 22px 24px;
    @include font-size(19, 24);
  }

  &:hover {
    .c-accordion__arrow {
      background-color: $gold;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/chevron-teal.png');
      border-color: $teal;
    }
  }

  &:active {
    .c-accordion__arrow {
      background-color: $gold;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/chevron-teal.png');
      border-color: $gold;
    }
  }

  &.show {
    .c-accordion__arrow {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
  }
}

.c-accordion__arrow {
  position: absolute;
  top: 13px;
  right: 16px;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas-house/assets/src/images/chevron-teal.png');
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
  background-size: 20px;
  transform: rotate(180deg);
  transition: color 300ms, background-color 300ms;
  pointer-events: none;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    top: 22px;
    right: 18px;
  }
}

.c-accordion__description {
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;

  transition: all 300ms;

  &-inner {
    padding: 10px 25px 18px 18px;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding: 10px 25px 25px 25px;
    }
  }

  p {
    @include font-size(19, 28);
    margin-top: 17px;
    margin-bottom: 0;

    &:first-of-type {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
  }

  ul,
  ol {
    @include font-size(16, 24);
    margin-top: 17px;
    margin-left: 17px;
  }

  a {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
}
",".c-donate__donation-type-wrapper {

  margin-bottom: 8px;
  padding: 1rem 0;
  background-color: $white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $blue;

  cursor: pointer;

  }

    color: $white;
    font-family: $font-text;
    font-weight: normal;
  }

",".c-card {
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  padding: 0 8px;
  text-decoration: none;

  @media (min-width: 400px) {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
    max-width: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: $break-tablet) {
    flex: 1 1 33%;
    max-width: 33%;
  }

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    flex: 1 1 25%;
    max-width: 25%;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
}

.c-card:last-child {
  margin-right: auto;
}

.c-card__inner {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 2px solid $light-grey;
  border-radius: 16px;
  transition: all 200ms;
}

.c-card__image {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 0;
  padding-bottom: 50%;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding-bottom: 60%;
  }

  &:after {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba($light-gold, 0.4);
    transition: all 200ms;
    opacity: 0;
    content: '';
  }
}

.c-card__actual-image {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.c-card__start-date {
  padding: 16px 80% 16px 16px;
  background-color: #bfe8f0;
  background-size: cover;
  color: $blue;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: all 200ms;
  @include font-size(56, 54);

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(72, 80);
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  &--image {
    background-color: unset;
    color: $white;
  }
}

.c-card__meta {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.c-card__terms {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
}

.c-card__term {
  margin-right: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  background-color: $light-gold;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(16, 20);
}

.c-card__charity {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 4px;
  margin-right: 8px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  background-color: $gold;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(16, 20);

  &--st-barnabas-house {
    background-color: $teal;
    color: $white;
  }
}

.c-card__location {
  @include font-size(16, 20);
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding: 8px 8px 0 24px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding-top: 12px;
  }

  &--onsite,
  &--virtual {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: contain;
  }

  &--onsite {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/address.svg');
  }

  &--virtual {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/virtual.svg');
  }
}

.c-card__content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  flex-grow: 1;
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 16px;
  padding-top: 32px;
  transition: all 200ms;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    padding-right: 24px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }
}

.c-card__header {
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  color: $blue;
  @include font-size(19, 22);

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(24, 28);
  }
}

.c-card__excerpt {
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(19, 26);

  p {
    @include font-size(19, 26);
  }
}

.c-card__address,
.c-card__opening-times {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding-left: 28px;
  color: $teal;
  font-family: $font-text;
  @include font-size(16, 20);

  &:before {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-right: 10px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }
}

.c-card__address {
  margin-top:12px;
  &:before {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/address.svg');
  }
}

.c-card__opening-times {
  &:before {
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/times.svg');
  }
}

.c-card__date {
  color: $teal;
  @include font-size(14, 18);
  font-family: $font-text;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    @include font-size(16, 20);
  }
}

.c-card__cta {
  display: flex;
  flex-basis:100%;
  align-items: flex-end;
  color: $blue;
  font-family: $font-text;
  font-weight: bold;
  @include font-size(19, 28);

  &:after {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-left: 10px;
    background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/st-barnabas/assets/src/images/cta-arrow.svg');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: contain;
    content: '';
  }
}

.c-card:hover {
  .c-card__inner {
    border-color: $blue;
  }

  .c-card__image {
    &:after {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .c-card__start-date {
    background-color: #bfe8f0;
  }

  .c-card__content {
    background-color: rgba($gold, 0.1);
  }
}

.c-card--2 {
  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
    max-width: 50%;
  }

  .c-card__image {
    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding-bottom: 190px;
    }
  }
}

.c-card--3 {
  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    flex: 1 1 33.33%;
    max-width: 33.33%;
  }

  .c-card__image {
    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding-bottom: 190px;
    }
  }
}

.c-card--long {
  display: block;
  flex: none;
  max-width: none;
  margin-bottom: 55px;

  .c-card__inner {
    flex-direction: row;
    height: auto;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .c-card__start-date,
  .c-card__image {
    display: none;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 244px;
      min-width: 244px;
      height: 182px;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
  }

  .c-card__content {
    padding: 0 8px;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      padding: 0 40px;
      border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    }
  }

  .c-card__header {
    @include font-size(24, 32);

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      @include font-size(32, 40);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
  }

  .c-card__excerpt {
    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
  }

  .c-card__type {
    display: inline-block;
    float: left;
    padding: 2px 8px 3px;
    background-color: $light-blue;
    border-radius: 5px;
    color: $teal;
    font-family: $font-text;
    @include font-size(16, 24);
  }

  .c-card__date {
    @include font-size(16, 28);
    float: left;
    margin-left: 24px;
  }
}

.c-card-event {
  position: relative;
}

.c-card-event__image-filter {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  z-index: -1;
  background-color: rgba($black, 0.2);
}

.c-card-event__image {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  z-index: -2;

    object-fit: cover;
  }

",".c-pagination {
  max-width: 1320px;
  margin: 20px auto 30px;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    margin-top: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
}

.c-pagination__list {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 12px;
  list-style: none;
}

.c-pagination__button {
  margin: 0 4px;

  a, span, button {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 60px;
    padding: 0 25px;
    background-color: $light-gold;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: $teal;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 200ms;
  }

  &:not(.disabled) {
    a, span, button {
      &:hover, &.current {
        background-color: $gold;
      }
    }
  }

  &.disabled {
    a, span, button {
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
  }

  i {
    display: none;
    font-style: normal;

    @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
      display: inline;
    }
  }
}

.c-pagination__number {
  display: none;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    display: flex;
  }
}

.c-pagination__prev, .c-pagination__next {
  width: 50%;

  @include breakpoint($break-desktop) {
    width: auto;
  }

  a, button {
    width: 100%;

    &:before, &:after {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background-image: url('/wp-content/themes/chestnut-tree-house/assets/src/images/btn_arrow.svg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center;
      background-size: contain;
      content: '';
    }
  }
}

.c-pagination__prev {
  a, button {
    &:before {
      margin-right: 14px;
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    &:after {
      display: none;
    }
  }
}

.c-pagination__next {
  a, button {
    &:before {
      display: none;
    }

    &:after {
      margin-left: 14px;
    }
  }
}
